                          |CKBChapter 5 - Newbie Areas
                      |BKB-----------------------------------

     |WKBThere are many areas with many themes for you to explore and gain
     experience and gold. I am sure I have not listed all of them, but I
     will continue to update this list as new ones are discovered and 
     reported to me. Two commands that will help you in your exploration
     are 'areas' and 'where'. The areas command will help you have a
     sense of where you can explore next. The where command when you're
     in an area exploring will help you decide if you should be there
     or not.
     
     |CKBAreas in Darkwind
     |BKB-----------------
     |WKBDirections are from COT

     |YKBAbandoned Village |BKB- 6w, exit, 4w, 2n, w, s, w, enter, n, w
     |YKOFarmers are about the most difficult thing in this area. Sentries will
     likely kill you if you attack them. Check for food in the vegetable
     patch.
          
     |YKBAshkenazy's hunting grounds |BKB- 5s, exit, s, 4w, s
     |YKOAshkenazy has made a hunting grounds for newbies of his experiments.
     |YKOLots of interesting and evil things to kill here.

     |YKBFarmland |BKB- |YKB6w, exit, 4w, 3n, 2e, n
     |YKOTypical farm animals. None of the creatures here are aggressive.
     
     |YKBGlaverton Forest |BKB- |YKB6w, exit, 4w, 2n, e, 3n, e, n, e, n, 5e,
                        2ne, nw, n
     |YKOThe forest south of Glaverton is apparently the abode of many tiny,
     but growing demons! They are ravaging the forest and killing forest
     creatures in an orgy of destruction as they grow. This area is 
     suitable for levels 1-10 of all alignments. None of the creatures
     are aggressive.
 
     |YKBHaunted Keep |BKB- |YKB5s, exit, 11s, w
     |YKORecommended for adventurers level 3 and up, or low level clerics and
     paladins. Undead minions have overrun this place.

     |YKBNorth Forest path |BKB- |YKB6n, exit ,9n, 9nw , w
     |YKOLarge amounts of wildlife through the forest for young adventurers to
     kill.

     |YKBPegasi |BKB- |YKB6n, exit, 8n, 2e, n
     |YKOBaby pegasi are not too difficult, but the mother is a challenge. This
     area is good for low level evil aligned players.
     
     |YKBPirate Ship |BKB- |YKB5e, 4n, climb rope (Note: This will take you into the bay)
     |YKOA pirate ship moored in the bay. Pirates have some food that will
     help you along the way. Do not be misled by the fact that you can
     swim safely in this bay. Most of the ocean is not so safe.
     
